<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM3.9">
<l>kañcaṉ valaivaitta vaṉṟu kāriru ḷelliṟ piḻaittu</l>
<l>neñcutuk kañceyyap pōntāy niṉṟavik kaṉṉiya rōmai</l>
<l>añca vurappā ḷacōtai yāṇāṭa viṭṭiṭ ṭirukkum</l>
<l>vañcakap pēyccipā luṇṭa macimaiyilī kūṟai tārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Escaping on a pitch black night when Kamsa set a trap,</l>
<l>You have set out to cause sorrow to the hearts of us maidens who stand here!</l>
<l>Yaśodā will not shout in such a way that [You] are afraid!</l>
<l rend="indent">She has let [You] do as [You] please!</l>
<l>O shameless Person who drank the deceitful demoness’s [breast] milk!</l>
<l rend="indent">Do give [us our] clothes!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
